NPCName "Harris"
Location "Crossroads"
Description "Harris is a patron of Sara's Place. He serves no purpose in the game other than to provide the PC with the Lucky Horseshoe item, which is part of the quest of the same name."
Unknown_Desc "You see a man happily nursing a bottle of beer."
Known_Desc "You see Harris. He is enjoying another beer."
Detailed_Desc "Many more empty bottles, similar to the half-full one he is holding, are grouped on the table in front of him."
/* Regular nodes */

Node "Har_0"
notes "Harris will only speak to the PC once, if he/she is dumb."
{
NPCText "*** STARTING CONDITIONS ***"
      options {
          int=1 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- The PC has never met Harris before -" linkto "Har_1a_1"  notes ""
          int=1 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- The PC has spoken to Harris before -" linkto "Har_1b_1"  notes ""
          int=1 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- The PC has bought a round of drinks in the bar where Harris is drinking -" linkto "Har_1c_1"  notes ""
          int=1 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- The PC has taken the Lucky Horseshoe from Harris -" linkto "Har_1b_1"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1a_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Hi, there."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hello, my name's <PC>. How about you?" linkto "Har_1a_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What's your story?" linkto "Har_1a_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Fuck off, bar-fly." linkto "Har_B1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Bye, there." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hello. You smell like beer." linkto "Har_1a_D1"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- LEAVE -" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1a_2a_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Good to meet you, <PC>. My name's Harris. Lend me ten caps and I'll buy you a drink."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What the hell - here's ten. Beer me." linkto "Har_1a_2a_2" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps >= 10 } notes "The screen fades to black and back. Decrement the number of caps owned by the PC by 10. Put a beer in the PC's inventory."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sure. Here's ten. Get me something non-alcoholic." linkto "Har_1a_2a_2" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps >= 10 } notes "The screen fades to black and back. Decrement the number of caps owned by the PC by 10. Put a Nuka-Cola in the PC's inventory."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Err... no. What's your story?" linkto "Har_1a_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Fuck off, bar-fly." linkto "Har_B1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No. 'Bye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1a_2a_2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "There you go, buddy. *He hands you your drink.*"
 NPCFemaleText "There you go, lady. *He hands you your drink.*"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So what's your story?" linkto "Har_1a_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks. See you later." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1a_2b_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "I've just finished work over at the cattle pens and I'm soaking up a few beers, that's my story."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Has anything interesting happened to you recently?" linkto "Har_1a_2b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll leave you to it." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1a_2b_2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Err... nope. Wait, a brahmin stood on Carl's foot the other day. Cracked me up the way he danced - funniest thing I have ever seen, I swear!"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "The things you guys must get up to. Well, I must be going." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll take that as a no, then. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1a_D1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "What?"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I smell beer once but Mommy said I not allowed drink it." linkto "Har_1a_D2"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- LEAVE -" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1a_D2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "A damn retard, that's all I need."
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I not a retard. I special. Mommy and Overseer say so." linkto "Har_1a_D3"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- LEAVE -" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1a_D3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Overseer? The hell you talking about, boy? What Overseer?"
 NPCFemaleText "Overseer? The hell you talking about, girl? What Overseer?"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Overseer run my home. Place where I come from." linkto "Har_1a_D4"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- LEAVE -" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1a_D4"
notes ""
{
NPCText "You mean an Overseer from a vault? *The man snorts a laugh, not sure whether to believe you.* You better not be messing with me, boy."
 NPCFemaleText "You mean an Overseer from a vault? *The man snorts a laugh, not sure whether to believe you.* You better not be messing with me, girl."
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I not lie. I tell you truth." linkto "Har_1a_D5_a1"  notes "Moderate speech check. IF failed, go to Har_1a_D5_b instead."
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- LEAVE -" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1a_D5_a1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Okay. Where is this vault of yours?"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*Point North.*" linkto "Har_1a_D5_a2"  notes "If the player chooses this option, it counts towards the number of times the PC reveals the location of Vault 31, which is needed to determine whether or not the Wasteland Explorers will be at the vault when the PC returns."
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*Point East.*" linkto "Har_1a_D5_a2"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*Point South.*" linkto "Har_1a_D5_a2"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*Point West.*" linkto "Har_1a_D5_a2"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- LEAVE -" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1a_D5_a2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Fancy that. *He turns away from you and takes a thoughtful swig from his beer bottle.* Fancy that."
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- LEAVE -" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1a_D5_b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*The man laughs again and this time a few nearby bar patrons join in.* Get lost, kid. This is no place for children to be playing in."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- LEAVE -" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1b_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Hello again. Fancy joining me for a drink? Your treat, I'm afraid - I'm stone broke."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Here's ten caps. Get me something non-alcoholic and whatever you're having." linkto "Har_1b_2" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps >= 10 } notes "The screen fades to black and back. Decrement the number of caps owned by the PC by 10. Put a Nuka-Cola in the PC's inventory."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Here's ten caps. Get me a beer and whatever you're having." linkto "Har_1b_2" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps >= 10 } notes "The screen fades to black and back. Decrement the number of caps owned by the PC by 10. Put a beer in the PC's inventory."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Fuck off, bar-fly." linkto "Har_B1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe another time. I have to be going." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1b_2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Thanks. Here's yours. *He hands you your drink.*"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Anything interesting happened since we last spoke?" linkto "Har_1b_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've just remembered I need to be somewhere else." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1b_3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Yeah, I've been watching that spider build that web. *He points with the neck of his beer-bottle at an intricate web strung between one of the bar-tent's poles and the canvas around it.* Fascinating creatures to watch."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- Watch the spider -" linkto "Har_1b_4"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've just remembered I need to be somewhere else." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1b_4"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*After a few minutes, the spider is seemingly satisfied with its work. It scuttles into the center of the web and begins waiting patiently for its first victim. Your drinking companion almosts startles you when he speaks again.* Amazing creatures."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yeah." linkto "Har_1b_5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've just remembered I need to be somewhere else." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
