Node "Har_1c_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Hey, thanks for the drink, buddy. Meant I could get a mug of the good stuff, instead of that bottled crap. I didn't know Sara was giving away free gifts with them, though."
 NPCFemaleText "Hey, thanks for the drink, lady.  Meant I could get a mug of the good stuff, instead of that bottled rubbish. I didn't know Sara was giving away free gifts with them, though."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Free gift? What do you mean?" linkto "Har_1c_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Neither did I. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1c_2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well, look. I found this plastic horseshoe thing in mine. *He holds up the horseshoe, which is small, florescent yellow, plastic and cheap-looking.*"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've been looking for that. May I have it?" linkto "Har_1c_3a_1"  notes "This node only appears if the PC has accepted the Lucky Horseshoe quest."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What are you going to do with it?" linkto "Har_1c_3b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Fancy that. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1c_3a_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Sure. Give me two caps and it's yours."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Here's your two caps." linkto "Har_1c_3a_2a" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps >= 2 } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It's not worth two caps. I'll give you one for it." linkto "Har_1c_3a_2b_a1"  notes "Mild barter check. IF failed, go to Har_1c_3a_2c instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Just give me the horseshoe before I pound your face into the dust." linkto "Har_1c_3B_a1"  notes "IF the PC's strength is less than 8, go to Har_1c_3B_b intead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No deal. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1c_3a_2a"
notes "Deduct two caps from the PC's inventory. Put the Lucky Horseshoe item in the PC's inventory."
{
NPCText "Here, take the damn thing. *He hands you the plastic horseshoe as he takes your money.*"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1c_3a_2b_a1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Heh. You gotta admit it was worth a try. Okay, gimmie a cap and you can have the damn thing."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Here. *Offer him a cap.*" linkto "Har_1c_3a_2b_a2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No deal. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1c_3a_2b_a2"
notes "Deduct one cap from the PC's inventory. Put the Lucky Horseshoe item in the PC's inventory."
{
NPCText "*He hands you the horseshoe. He balances the cap he takes from you in return on the end of his thumb, flicks it into the air, and catches it again, before putting it into his pocket.*"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Nice. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1c_3a_2c"
notes ""
{
NPCText "No, I reckon you'll give me two for it."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay, here's your two caps." linkto "Har_1c_3a_2a" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps >= 2 } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It's not worth two caps. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1c_3b"
notes "Spawn the Lucky Horseshoe on the ground, a hex or two behind Harris."
{
NPCText "I sure as hell don't want it in my drink, I know that much. *He throws it over his shoulder.*"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll leave you to it." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1c_3B_a1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Hey, don't be so hasty! Take the damn thing."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*Take the horseshoe.* There, that wasn't so bad, was it?" linkto "Har_1c_3B_a2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1c_3B_a2"
notes "Put the Lucky Horseshoe item in the PC's inventory.\nHarris will no longer speak to the PC. He will still float the text relating to the Lucky Horseshoe quest if the PC buys a round of drinks, though."
{
NPCText "*He turns back to his drink, muttering.* I thought those things were supposed to bring you GOOD luck..."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- LEAVE -" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1c_3B_b1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*He gives you an exaggerated frown and his voice rises through an octave of disbelief.* What the HELL did you just say? *The other patrons in the bar-tent look round eagerly, hoping for a fight.*"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Don't mess with me, pal. Just hand over the horseshoe." linkto "combat"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay, forget I mentioned it." linkto "Har_1c_3B_b2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_1c_3B_b2"
notes "Harris will no longer speak to the PC. He will still float the text relating to the Lucky Horseshoe quest if the PC buys a round of drinks, though."
{
NPCText "*you receive a chorus of chicken noises from the patrons as you back down.*"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That does it. *Draw weapon.*" linkto "combat"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*Cringe and leave*" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_B1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "What did you just say, pal?"
 NPCFemaleText "What did you just say, lady?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I told you to fuck off and I called you a bar-fly. So fuck off, bar-fly." linkto "Har_B2_a"  notes "IF the PC's strength is below 8, go to Har_B2_b instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I said, \"my, doesn't time fly?\" I've got to be going, goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_B2_a"
notes "Harris will no longer speak to the PC. He will still float the text relating to the Lucky Horseshoe quest if the PC buys a round of drinks, though."
{
NPCText "Geez, can't a guy enjoy his beer in peace? Okay, I won't bother you again."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Make sure you don't." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Har_B2_b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "You're mixing it up with the wrong 'bar-fly', pal. *He puts his glass down with a thump on the table. The other patrons in the bar-tent look round eagerly, hoping for a fight.*"
 NPCFemaleText "You're mixing it up with the wrong 'bar-fly', lady. I ain't above teaching a smart-mouthed bitch like you some manners. *He puts his glass down with a thump on the table. The other patrons in the bar look round eagerly, hoping for a fight.*"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wait, you're not going to hit me, are you?" linkto "combat"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let's see what you've got, asshole." linkto "combat"  notes ""
              }
}
